application_type_full: Prior Approval: Change of use - offices to dwellinghouses
description: Prior approval for change of use of part ground, 1st to 8th floors, part of the 9th floor and 10th to 14th floors from office (Use Class B1) to residential (Use Class C3) involving the creation of either 353 residential units, with cycle storage for 356 full size cycles (this storage is split with 76 spaces provide within the ground floor entrance foyer area and 280 spaces in a store area at first floor level) or 360 residential units, with capacity for the storage of 76 full size cycles within the ground floor foyer area (with the addition of external cycle stores), and communal facilities including a gym and lounge at the 15th floor.
